" Key bindings like Emacs
"" Normal mode + Visual mode
noremap <C-f> <Right>
noremap <C-b> <Left>
noremap <C-a> <Home>
noremap <C-e> <End><Right>
noremap <C-n> <Down>
noremap <C-p> <Up>

"" Commandline mode + Insert mode
noremap! <C-f> <Right>
noremap! <C-b> <Left>
noremap! <C-a> <Home>
noremap! <C-e> <End><Right>
noremap! <C-n> <Down>
noremap! <C-p> <Up>
noremap! <C-c> <Right><Esc>
